()1️⃣ IdentityNow me users kaha se aate hain?
Users normally kisi source system se aate hain.
Example:-
Active Directory
HR System
Database
Workday
Jab aggregation hoti hai tab users import ho jate hain.

Flow:-
HR System / AD
      ↓
Aggregation
      ↓
IdentityNow
      ↓
Users create ho jate hain

2️⃣ Example:-
HR system me record hai:-
EmployeeID : 1001
Name : Rahul
Email : rahul@company.com
Aggregation ke baad IdentityNow me record banega:-
{
 "id": "2c9180847e9b1a1f017e9c1111111111",
 "name": "Rahul",
 "email": "rahul@company.com"
}

Isi tarah:-

{
 "id": "2c9180847e9b1a1f017e9c3333333333",
 "name": "Amit"
}
