()access-profiles ids kaha se milti hai?
--1️⃣ Access Profile IDs kaha se milti hain
Method 1: API se (Most common):-
API call:-
GET /v3/access-profiles
Java example:-
import java.net.HttpURLConnection;
import java.net.URL;
import java.io.BufferedReader;
import java.io.InputStreamReader;

public class GetAccessProfiles {

    public static void main(String[] args) throws Exception {

        URL url = new URL("https://tenant.api.identitynow.com/v3/access-profiles");

        HttpURLConnection conn = (HttpURLConnection) url.openConnection();

        conn.setRequestMethod("GET");
        conn.setRequestProperty("Authorization", "Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN");

        BufferedReader br = new BufferedReader(
                new InputStreamReader(conn.getInputStream()));

        String line;

        while ((line = br.readLine()) != null) {
            System.out.println(line);
        }
    }
}
2️⃣ Example Output:-
System response:-
[
 {
  "id": "2c9180847e9b1a1f017e9c2222222222",
  "name": "Salesforce Read Access"
 },
 {
  "id": "2c9180847e9b1a1f017e9c4444444444",
  "name": "SAP Finance Access"
 }
]
Yaha se milta hai:-
Access Profile Name → Salesforce Read Access
Access Profile ID → 2c9180847e9b1a1f017e9c2222222222



